data.description: Immaculate end-unit townhome in highly sought-after community of Terraces of Stonecrest! The open-concept design features high ceilings, hardwood floors, and a bay window in the dining area, offering more natural light than an interior unit. Enjoy cooking your favorite recipes in the galley-style kitchen, equipped with all appliances, granite countertops, tile backsplash, and a large pass-thru window to the living space. The huge upstairs loft provides valuable flex space for a home office, 2nd living area, or bonus room of your choice! All bedrooms are located upstairs with laundry for your convenience. Relax and retreat to the spacious owner's suite, boasting a cathedral ceiling, large walk-in closet, and a sprawling master bath with dual vanity, soaking tub, and separate shower. The backyard comes with full privacy fence, patio, and sizable awning--perfect outdoor space for grilling and entertaining guests. Rich in amenities, Terraces of Stonecrest is a newer townhome community with tennis courts, in-ground swimming pool, playground, and more! Don't miss out on this unique opportunity--schedule your showing today!
